<h2>London Overground</h2>
<p>On Monday 27 August, a Saturday service will run on London Overground routes not affected by closures. An amended Saturday service will run on routes with closures:</p>
<h3>Gospel Oak - Barking route</h3>
<p>From Saturday 25 August until Monday 27 August, there will be no service between South Tottenham and Barking. Use the Victoria line between Seven Sisters (for South Tottenham) and Walthamstow Central or local buses. Replacement bus services will run between Walthamstow Central and Barking.</p>
<h3>Liverpool Street - Enfield Town / Cheshunt / Chingford route</h3>
<p>On Sunday 26 August until 10:15, there will be no service between Liverpool Street and Enfield Town / Cheshunt (via Seven Sisters) / Chingford. Use local buses or Tube services between Liverpool Street and Seven Sisters/Hackney Downs. Replacement bus services will run between Seven Sisters and Enfield Town / Cheshunt and between Hackney Downs and Chingford.</p>
<h3>Watford Junction - Euston route</h3>
<p>On Saturday 25 August and Sunday 26 August, there will be no service between Euston and Watford Junction. Use the Bakerloo line between Queen's Park and Stonebridge Park. Replacement bus services will run between Stonebridge Park and Harrow &amp; Wealdstone / Watford Junction.</p>
<p>On Monday 27 August, there will be no service between Euston and Kilburn High Road. Please use local buses or Tube services.</p>
<h3>Highbury &amp; Islington - West Croydon / Clapham Junction route</h3>
<p>From Saturday 25 August until Monday 27 August there will be no service between Surrey Quays and Clapham Junction. Replacement bus services will run.</p>
<h3>Clapham Junction - Stratford route</h3>
<p>On Sunday 26 August until 11:15, there will be no service between Clapham Junction and Willesden Junction. Please use local buses.</p>
